* Tumai Salih<ref name=autogenerated1>{{cite web |title=Lamborghini by KSI featuring P Money |url=https://listen.tidal.com/album/86036682/track/86036683 |website=Tidal |accessdate=16 February 2020}}</ref>\n| producer   = DJ Turkish<ref name=autogenerated1 />\n| chronology = [[KSI (entertainer)|KSI]]\n| prev_title = No Sleep\n| prev_year  = 2013\n| next_title = [[Keep Up (KSI song)|Keep Up]]\n| next_year  = 2015\n| misc       = {{Extra chronology\n | artist     = [[P Money]]\n | type       = Singles\n | prev_title = Reload\n | prev_year  = 2012\n | title      = Lamborghini\n | year       = 2015\n | next_title = 10/10\n | next_year  = 2015\n}}\n{{External music video|{{YouTube|708mjaHTwKc|\"Lamborghini\"}}}}\n}}\n\n\"'''Lamborghini'''\" is the debut song by English YouTube personality and rapper [[KSI (entertainer)|KSI]], featuring English grime MC [[P Money]]. The song is produced by DJ Turkish. It was released on 23 March 2015 through [[Dcypha Productions]]. The song charted at number 30 on the [[UK Singles Chart]].<ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/jess-glynne-scores-her-first-solo-number-1__8805/|title=\u201cIt\u2019s a pretty insane feeling!\u201d Jess Glynne scores first solo Number 1|website=www.officialcharts.com|language=en|access-date=2020-02-16}}</ref>\n\n== Commercial performance ==\nThe song entered the UK Singles Chart at number 30, making it KSI's first UK top 40 single and his third highest charting single in the UK to date.<ref name=\":0\" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/artist/48106/ksi/|title=KSI {{!}} full Official Chart History {{!}} Official Charts Company|website=www.officialcharts.com|access-date=2020-03-27}}</ref> It dropped to number 68 and number 96 over the following two weeks before dropping out of the top 100.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/singles-chart/20150405/7501/|title=Official Singles Chart Top 100 {{!}} Official Charts Company|website=www.officialcharts.com|language=en|access-date=2020-02-16}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/singles-chart/20150412/7501/|title=Official Singles Chart Top 100 {{!}} Official Charts Company|website=www.officialcharts.com|language=en|access-date=2020-02-16}}</ref> KSI reacted to the commercial success of the song on [[Twitter]], saying \"yo thanks to everyone who listened to Lamborghini on Spotify and bought on iTunes!!! Didn't even think I would get in the top 40 man\".<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://teneightymagazine.com/2015/04/04/ksi-enters-uk-top-40/|title=KSI Enters UK Top 40 \u2013 TenEighty \u2014 YouTube News, Features, and Interviews|language=en-GB|access-date=2020-02-16}}</ref>\n\n==Music video==\nThe music video, directed by Jak X, was uploaded to KSI's YouTube channel on 25 March 2015, two days after the release of the song. KSI's purple [[Lamborghini Aventador]] prominently appears in the video. As of April 2020, the music video has 110 million views, making it KSI's most-viewed music video on YouTube to date.<ref name=\"Music video\">{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=708mjaHTwKc|title=KSI - Lamborghini (Explicit) feat. P Money|publisher=[[YouTube]] |date=25 March 2015|accessdate=26 March 2015}}</ref>\n\n== Remix ==\nA remixed version of the song, which does not feature P Money and instead features new verses by KSI and English rappers [[Sway (musician)|Sway]], Youngs Teflon and [[Scrufizzer]], appears on KSI's 2016 debut extended play ''[[Keep Up (EP)|Keep Up]]'' under the name \"Lambo Refuelled\".\n\n== Track listing ==\n{{Track listing\n| headline = Digital download<ref name=autogenerated2 />\n| title6 = \n| length10 = \n| title10 = \n| length9 = \n| title9 = \n| length8 = \n| title8 = \n| length7 = \n| title7 = \n| length6 = \n| length5 = \n| title1 = Lamborghini\n| title5 = \n| length4 = \n| title4 = \n| length3 = \n| title3 = \n| length2 = \n| title2 = \n| all_writing = \n| length1 = 2:56\n| note1 = featuring [[P Money]]